data.description: $11k OFFERED TOWARDS A 2/1 RATE BUY DOWN. Welcome to this meticulously maintained 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 3 car garage, Perry Home. Located in Fronterra at Westpointe, a highly sought after neighborhood that offers the convenience of a high school on-site. Step inside and you'll be immediately captivated by the high ceilings, open floor plan, tile flooring, and an abundance of natural light that floods the home and creates an inviting ambiance. The second bedroom provides the perfect space for a home office or library in combination with the bedroom. This bedroom is also pre-wired for surround sound adding even more potential. The large open kitchen features beautiful shaker cabinets, a gas cooktop, convection oven, stainless steel appliances and ample space for food prep, making it a dream come true for any home chef. The beautiful mosaic backsplash and granite countertops add a touch of elegance to the space, along with the open concept living room, making it the perfect place to prepare meals and entertain guests. The master bedroom offers a relaxing retreat with tall windows. The master bathroom features a walk-in shower, a corner garden tub, separate vanities, and a large walk-in closet, providing ample space for all your storage needs. You'll find an additional bedroom with ensuite bathroom in the middle of the house. The gigantic backyard is a true oasis, featuring a covered patio with fans where you can grill and enjoy the Texas weather year-round. An additional 31-foot cement pad runs along the right-side of the home, and is perfect for rain capture or additional outdoor storage. The left side of the backyard offers additional space and a double-door gate to store a small trailer or fishing boat. The finished three-car garage with professionally installed epoxy flooring has an extended bump-out perfect for a workbench or storage area. Close to JBSA-Lackland, Sea World, Six Flags, shopping, restaurants, and everything that San Antonio and the surrounding areas have to offer. In summary, this home provides comfort and space, featuring stylish design elements and practical amenities that make it a perfect place to call home. Priced below tax assessor value, this home will go fast, so don't miss out on this opportunity to live in this immaculate property.
